<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
  <% include ../partials/head %>
  </head>
  <body>
  <header>
    <h1>
      Diceware App: Rolling, Rolling Rolling Your Own!!
    </h1>
    <p>
        Use the fields below to enter your dice rolls and we'll give you the word
        for your passphrase.
